Class NetworkStatsCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.server.net.NetworkStatsCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileRotator.Reader

    public class NetworkStatsCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileRotator.Reader
    Collection of NetworkStatsHistory, stored based on combined key of NetworkIdentitySet, UID, set, and tag. Knows how to persist itself.
